Package: hotShiny
Type: Package
Title: Shiny-Compatible Reactive Framework with Hot Reloading
Version: 0.1.0
Author: HotShiny Contributors
Maintainer: HotShiny Contributors <maintainer@hotshiny.example>
Description: A Shiny-compatible R package that supports hot-reloading by
    transforming Shiny's execution model into a declarative, diffable reactive
    graph. Maintains API compatibility while fundamentally changing runtime semantics.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
